cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with text categorization, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of clustering algorithms and feature representation techniques also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the reduction of dimensionality, which is a common problem in data science (cs.DS).
